description:
Danny recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules and Real Housewives of Atlanta. On Vanderpump Rules, Scheana makes up with Dayna and gives her the gift of a reading, James and Lala hit up the recording studio, and the Witches of Weho continue to feud. On the RHOA finale, Kandi and T*dd throw a baby shower, Kenya talks to TMZ, while Nene talks to Wendy Williams.


RHOA: 25:00ish


YOUTUBE: https://www.youtube.com/dannypellegrino1

For tickets to the Chicago live show: https://bit.ly/3bc6QLX
